name: "Victim" by RFY (HF) & FEH
description: [Brush pen and felt pen on paper bag with digital embellishments and color.] This piece is a beautiful collab with my not-quite-2-year-old granddaughter, Felicity. I drew the face on this bag puppet, and Felicity made him the victim of a vicious serial killer! HA! Brilliant work, kid... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Toddler Artist)
